##PROMPT AND SOME TIPS FOR ACCOUNT CREATION


Name prompt - 
Suggest short, catchy, unique, and brandable names for an Instagram page focused on [NICHE]. The names should be a maximum of 2–3 words,
easy to remember, pronounce, and spell, and should have a modern, trendy feel that aligns with the intended audience and content style.
Avoid common or overused names, and ensure each suggestion feels distinctive, original, and capable of growing into a strong brand identity. 
Provide 10–20 creative name options that are not generic and reflect the theme, vibe, and purpose of the page.


Bio prompt - 
Write an Instagram bio for a page focused on [NICHE]. The bio should be exactly four lines long and between 146–150 characters in total. 
Use a mix of emojis and text in an "emoji | text" format to make it visually appealing and engaging. 
Keep the tone aligned with the niche and target audience, ensuring it feels modern, catchy, and relevant.
The bio should clearly reflect the theme, purpose, and value of the page while remaining concise, creative, and memorable.


Tagline prompt - 
Suggest short, catchy, and niche-relevant taglines for an Instagram page focused on [NICHE].
The tagline should clearly communicate what kind of content is posted (e.g., clips, facts, updates, news, discoveries, etc.) while remaining concise and engaging. 
Keep it under 8–12 words, easy to understand, and aligned with the theme of the niche. 
The tone should match the content style (informative, fun, aesthetic, bold, or trendy), and the wording should feel natural, not overly promotional. 
Provide 10–15 tagline options that are simple, clear, and memorable.


