Three pinned post prompt -
Introduction prompt :
Write an engaging Instagram introduction post for a page named [PAGE NAME], focused on [NICHE], in a bold, high-energy, and immersive style similar to a brand launch or welcome post. 
Start with a powerful headline in all caps with emojis (e.g., “WELCOME TO [PAGE NAME] — [TAGLINE/HOOK]”), followed by aesthetic spacing using dots or line breaks. 
Then write a compelling paragraph explaining what the page is about, including the type of content (such as clips, updates, tips, highlights, etc.), and build excitement by describing the experience, emotions, or value the audience will get.
Include a section starting with “Expect:” followed by 3–5 clean, short lines (each on a new line) describing what the audience will see, using emojis if needed but without using the “emoji | text” format. End with a strong closing statement that creates a sense of belonging, hype, or identity (e.g., “Welcome to the movement”). 
Keep the tone energetic, bold, slightly dramatic, and engaging, making it feel like a brand rather than just a page. Use vivid, niche-relevant language, clean spacing, and ensure the content is impactful, scroll-stopping, and adaptable by replacing placeholders with the appropriate niche details.

